data.rationale:
This module is equipped for writing SWF (Macromedia Flash(R) movie)
    file. The name 'SWF' seems a new rootlevel namespace. 'SWF' is a
    file format name like 'HTML', 'PDF', 'PostScript', etc. They are
    rootlevel, so 'SWF' is suitable for rootlevel, I think.
